Describe a Report

Give your report a description to help people (and yourself) distinguish it.

Available in: both Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience
Available in: Group, Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions
Available in: Enhanced Folder Sharing

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
Create and Customize Reports or Report Builder or Report Builder (Lightning Experience)

Edit a report.
Open the properties menu.
In Lightning Experience, next to the Save button, click Properties.
In Salesforce Classic, click Report Properties.
Under Report Description, give your report a helpful description.
Click Save.

The reportâ€™s description is updated.
